{"tid":117073,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係已經好攰","createTime":"2017-02-12T01:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T06:50:10.000Z","uid":209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea221a76996b162ef95196388083941d07f8c2f5","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:41:58.000Z","msg":"點解所有野 都唔如意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做人真係好攰"},{"pid":"11948739f8895b775f886a7a716a864de6125ae8","tid":117073,"uid":3627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想忘記過去"},{"pid":"77ed9c1a90adaf101a8ef54b0ebc3b5ba73682f9","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:45:53.000Z","msg":"一次又一次咁 失望 係幾咁辛苦同痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e5dd0c375eb61194cd05f78889e3e3a68d26a2","tid":117073,"uid":10169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一次又一次咁 失望 係幾咁辛苦同痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好絕望"},{"pid":"83ed556ea5526223089655dd78862ea66e3b8450","tid":117073,"uid":3627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:51:32.000Z","msg":"崩潰過後又一條好漢<br />\n但我做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bb4dc0a61eb183deaab065ee918b6f09b45101","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一次又一次咁 失望 係幾咁辛苦同痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好絕望</blockquote><br />\n仲要發現呢啲時候無人會 care 自己<br />\n枉自己平時人地有咩唔開心都會認真去開解<br />\n好似永遠我既問題就唔係問題咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbf00bb4b5160d13ad0a597f36334783ce87b5d","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>崩潰過後又一條好漢<br />\n但我做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想知我前世做錯咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可能係我應得既"},{"pid":"835fb64ca9908da2e2e6e8d3ab32140b1cd5a217","tid":117073,"uid":3627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一次又一次咁 失望 係幾咁辛苦同痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好絕望</blockquote><br />\n仲要發現呢啲時候無人會 care 自己<br />\n枉自己平時人地有咩唔開心都會認真去開解<br />\n好似永遠我既問題就唔係問題咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲人成日覺得你平時都好穩陣架啦洗咩理咁多，但其實........自己都係普通人，會笑亦都會喊"},{"pid":"112e71892fff05ef37cd027cf70e849cc832cacf","tid":117073,"uid":834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:59:52.000Z","msg":"講出黎<br />\n緊張你既人就會去關心你<br />\n<br />\n有時捱過左就否極泰來 好似係咁"},{"pid":"e821ede8f82a9c977477ad3e3d60078903cac497","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講出黎<br />\n緊張你既人就會去關心你<br />\n<br />\n有時捱過左就否極泰來 好似係咁</blockquote><br />\n真係唔覺得有人係緊張自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736f00a0cde582b998f75f48bdf51744006d32bf","tid":117073,"uid":834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T02:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講出黎<br />\n緊張你既人就會去關心你<br />\n<br />\n有時捱過左就否極泰來 好似係咁</blockquote><br />\n真係唔覺得有人係緊張自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好朋友呢？<br />\n<br />\n冇唔緊要 你仲有依到傾訴"},{"pid":"37f2f70bf3fde3b62ad6f322d1148dc96996c424","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講出黎<br />\n緊張你既人就會去關心你<br />\n<br />\n有時捱過左就否極泰來 好似係咁</blockquote><br />\n真係唔覺得有人係緊張自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好朋友呢？<br />\n<br />\n冇唔緊要 你仲有依到傾訴</blockquote><br />\n好似一講唔開心野就好煩<br />\n同埋係解決唔到 有時我只係想不停呻下<br />\n但驚覺得好煩 所以唔敢成日講"},{"pid":"d48724c204935c7e09537fa4c92f0dcd95210b2e","tid":117073,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cfcfe52a63afe1c213f05a1cd7edc6543ec81a","tid":117073,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"一齊去死好唔好"},{"pid":"5d7eddd3077f0e84faaf20790d58ebc028d93b8d","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊去死好唔好</blockquote><br />\n點死舒服啲"},{"pid":"0f6830a8e4c2432ad3c0985293f010e74648b42a","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e439a4b241cf5951f9cde53d782a0f4a86db58","tid":117073,"uid":3627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講出黎<br />\n緊張你既人就會去關心你<br />\n<br />\n有時捱過左就否極泰來 好似係咁</blockquote><br />\n真係唔覺得有人係緊張自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好朋友呢？<br />\n<br />\n冇唔緊要 你仲有依到傾訴</blockquote><br />\n好似一講唔開心野就好煩<br />\n同埋係解決唔到 有時我只係想不停呻下<br />\n但驚覺得好煩 所以唔敢成日講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己知自己係一個好煩既人，又好多負能量。但不停咁樣呻身邊既朋友都會唔開心，真係好憎自己"},{"pid":"d1d23ad1cea1c682fac33222157a54580b63b465","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講出黎<br />\n緊張你既人就會去關心你<br />\n<br />\n有時捱過左就否極泰來 好似係咁</blockquote><br />\n真係唔覺得有人係緊張自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好朋友呢？<br />\n<br />\n冇唔緊要 你仲有依到傾訴</blockquote><br />\n好似一講唔開心野就好煩<br />\n同埋係解決唔到 有時我只係想不停呻下<br />\n但驚覺得好煩 所以唔敢成日講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己知自己係一個好煩既人，又好多負能量。但不停咁樣呻身邊既朋友都會唔開心，真係好憎自己</blockquote><br />\n收埋算啦 已經無乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無人真係會關心自己"},{"pid":"4c5928064e89079b126e27d1b0e53101db4b23a9","tid":117073,"uid":209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899d56dfd0013821bd9a1d678c2e5c5ff8d523a6","tid":117073,"uid":25432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"唔好咁樣諗 我而家都同你一樣 思緒好凌亂<br />\n人生不如意事 十常八九 放眼未來 總會有出口<br />\n共勉之"}]}